        "id": 1408114,
        "body": "This was great fun. I saw a trailer to this a year before it released and it definitely peaked my interest. I ended up playing it day one on game pass. Unfortunately I didn’t sleep that night. I was too busy trying to beat this game. <br/><br/>As soon as everything kicks off. It dosent stop. The game likes to throw you into a curveball. That by the end honestly made me shocked. The ending was something I would have never ever expected. James McAvoy was brilliant in his role and so was Willem Defoe and Daisy Ridley. <br/><br/>Great indie game. Love to see more from the dev at some point in the near future. <br/><br/>Date Completed: 11/09/2021<br/>Time spent on the game: 12 hours, 16 minutes<br/>Rating: 8.5/10",
